---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact | Combat Design Portfolio">
  <section class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-blue-700">Contact</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black text-slate-950">欢迎预约面试或索取私有材料访问方式</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-600">请将以下占位信息替换为正式邮箱、LinkedIn、作品集域名或招聘平台资料。</p>
    <dl class="mt-8 grid gap-4 text-slate-700 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-5"><dt class="font-semibold text-slate-950">Email</dt><dd class="mt-1">hello@example.com</dd></div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-5"><dt class="font-semibold text-slate-950">Portfolio Access</dt><dd class="mt-1">Restricted case studies require a preview code.</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
